cs.ET, cs.AR, cs.PL, cs.LO, cs.SE

This paper introduces a new programming language and compiler for expressing reversibility and energy efficiency in algorithm design and implementation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.ET (Emerging Technologies), which includes papers on new programming languages and paradigms. The paper also discusses the design and implementation of the language and compiler, which falls under cs.AR (Architecture), cs.PL (Programming Languages), and cs.SE (Software Engineering). Finally, the paper introduces many powerful control logic operators, which could also place it in the cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) category.
